messages.content: ComfyUI-RuiquNodes is a set of custom nodes for ComfyUI that includes EvaluateMultiple1, EvaluateMultiple3, and other nodes.
ComfyUI-RuiquNodes supports the execution of any fragment of Python code, allowing for the generation of multiple outputs from multiple inputs.
Can ComfyUI-RuiquNodes execute Python code snippets?
Yes, ComfyUI-RuiquNodes has the capability to execute any fragment of Python code.
How many outputs can ComfyUI-RuiquNodes generate from multiple inputs?
ComfyUI-RuiquNodes can generate multiple outputs from multiple inputs.
Is EvaluateMultiple1 a node included in ComfyUI-RuiquNodes?
Yes, EvaluateMultiple1 is one of the nodes included in the ComfyUI-RuiquNodes set.
Does ComfyUI-RuiquNodes include the EvaluateMultiple3 node?
Yes, EvaluateMultiple3 is a node that is part of the ComfyUI-RuiquNodes collection.
Are ComfyUI-RuiquNodes custom nodes specifically designed for ComfyUI?
Yes, ComfyUI-RuiquNodes are custom nodes that are specifically created to extend the functionality of ComfyUI.
